title: "The Eval Trap: Why Measurement Isn't Optimization"
slug: "the-eval-trap"
date: "2026-05-15"
summary: "Evaluation frameworks tell you how each configuration scored. They don't tell you which configuration to try next, search the configuration space, or refine your benchmark over time. Eval is necessary ŌĆö but it's not sufficient for ROI."
